01:03:27.541 --> 01:03:28.858
Seersant.

669
01:03:30.208 --> 01:03:31.508
Seersant.

670
01:03:44.791 --> 01:03:46.091
Seersant!

671
01:03:54.541 --> 01:03:56.333
Toimetame soomuki maapinnale.

672
01:03:56.916 --> 01:03:58.508
Kõik liikvele!

673
