798
01:21:13.458 --> 01:21:16.508
Sa arvad. et vedasid oma venda alt?

799
01:21:17.875 --> 01:21:19.875
Ma vedasin kõiki alt.

800
01:21:20.958 --> 01:21:22.708
Aga sa ei andnud iial alla.

801
01:21:24.416 --> 01:21:26.400
See pole altvedamine.

802
01:21:28.458 --> 01:21:30.933
See on reindþerlik käitumine.

803
