Kivid?

814
01:23:53.500 --> 01:23:55.358
Kivipurusti.

815
01:23:55.458 --> 01:23:57.791
Kuidas see sisse lülitatakse?

816
01:24:14.333 --> 01:24:16.375
Termodünaamika. litapoeg.

817
01:26:05.849 --> 01:26:07.376
DÜNAMIIT

818
01:26:22.708 --> 01:26:24.166
Tule!

819
