Ei!

822
01:27:19.833 --> 01:27:21.150
Jäta jama!

823
01:27:21.958 --> 01:27:23.333
Ei-ei!

824
01:27:43.125 --> 01:27:44.625
Hinga. raibe!

825
01:27:46.583 --> 01:27:48.100
Hermeetik. libu.

826
01:28:17.958 --> 01:28:19.333
Jah!

827
01:28:24.958 --> 01:28:26.366
Pea vastu!

828
01:29:37.750 --> 01:29:39.291
